text: Fractolatirus is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Fasciolariidae, the spindle snails, the tulip snails and their allies. ==Species== Species within the genus Fractolatirus include: * Fractolatirus normalis Iredale, 1936 ==References== Category:Fasciolariidae Category:Monotypic gastropod genera
title: Fractolatirus
